headline: Assessing Dell Technologies (DELL) Valuation After Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: Dell Technologies (DELL) has drawn fresh attention after its recent share price pullback, with the stock down about 5% over the past month and about 19% over the past 3 months. See our latest analysis for Dell Technologies. That pullback comes after a strong run, with Dell’s 1 year total shareholder return of 11.93% and very large 3 and 5 year total shareholder returns.
